  <summary date="2022-01-03T18:49:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Employee Privacy Act

This bill prohibits employers from inquiring about the vaccination status of employees or prospective employees.

Violations of this prohibition are subject to civil penalties, special damages, and injunctive relief as appropriate.</summary>
